{
  "id": "class_0027",
  "name": "Salt-Charted Cartomancer",
  "title_completion": "a Salt-Charted Cartomancer",
  "flavor_text": "The Cartographer's Tower gave you ink made of brine and a map that rewrites itself with every gust. You do not navigate the world \u2014 you dissolve its edges until only your meridians remain. Where others see coastline, you see a wound waiting to be salted.",
