      ],
      "flavor_text": "A bitter salt-laden wind unfurls from the tower's apex, rewriting the air itself into a sweeping cone of crystalline water that scours flesh and memory alike. What stood mapped is now dissolved, its coordinates erased in a single drenching breath."
